Recipe Calculator: Privacy policy

Welcome to the Recipe Calculator app for Android!

This is an Android app developed by Jani Veble, the app is available on Google Play.

I have not programmed this app to collect any personally identifiable information. All data (app preferences, recipes etc.) generated by your use of the app is stored on your device only, and can be simply deleated by uninstalling the app.

If you find any security vulnerability that has been inadvertently caused by this app, or have any question regarding how the app protects your privacy, please send me an email and I will surely try to address your concerns.

Yours sincerely,

Jani Veble

learning.indie@gmail.com
